oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Ransom McKibbin
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A portrait photograph of a black man, seated, with two children, a boy, in a hat, and a girl, in long sleeved dress, standing behind him. The man is likely Ransom McKibbin, based on a typed description on the reverse.
